verbose_text: To enable SPR studies, an AviTagTM sequence (GLNDIFEAQKIEWHE) was introduced at the N-terminal end of gamma-subunit (alpha1beta1gamma1, alpha1beta2gamma1, alpha2beta2gamma1 and alpha2beta2gamma3) and co-expressed with biotin-ligase (BirA) in E. coli.
